comment: The data appears to be available only to the scientists, not the players of the game.
It seems they haven't yet established an Ownership Policy, since they have a forum devoted to deciding this right now: http://fold.it/portal/node/992792

In the sense that Fold It produces scientific knowledge it could be argued that players collectively obtain the resource, along with all humans, but not in any legal sense.   Publication credit has been offered for contributions.
